<p><strong>JA Mendozite Template</strong> for Joomla 2.5 & 3.2</p>

<p>Impress your business partners with a clean, simple and well-organized business profile. The design for JA Mendozite is clean and clear 
but yet fully functioned.</p>
<p>With JA Mendozite, you get hands on the version of Joomla 2.5, J3.2 and K2 component. The famous T3 Framework is back in this business 
template along with the new Slideshow Lite module and Kunena forum. All in one template, JA Mendozite is surely business-oriented and will fit 
to all kinf of business projects.</p>
<p>Note: This template does not support RTL CSS style</p>
